 <TT>Interessante Lyrics</TT><P>

  Passend zum Oldie Review in der aktuellen Ausgabe, habe ich mir auch für
 diese Rubrik einen Song vom selben Longplayer (&quot;Death Or Glory&quot;; 1989)
 ausgesucht. Die Thematik hatten wir zwar schonmal in ähnlicher Form
 (Stratovarius), aber ich denke mal, daß man nicht häufig genug drauf
 hinweisen kann.<P>

 <I>Fifty Years Ago With The World At War Hands Bloodied - devastated Better
 Believe They Are Back For More Pounding The World With A Fist Of Steel
 Jack Booted, Heavy Handed Careless Of The Pain We Feel<P>

 Bridge: Bastards - Throwing Life Away Killers - Alive Today<P>

 Refrain: Oh Oh Oh Oh Don`t Tell No Lies I See Through Your Eyes You Are
 Bad To The Bone Oh Oh Oh Oh Don`t Tell No Lies You Can`t Hear The Cries
 `Cos You`re Bad To The Bone<P>

 Times Have Changed But He Don`t Know Zoot Suit, Black Tie Careless That
 The Lies Are Low One For All And All For One Talking Smooth - Hidden Truth
 Time Bomb Ticking Just Begun<P>

 Bridge<P>

 Refrain<P>

 Standing Alone For The World To See Non - Starter, Push Harder He Still
 Believes His Time Will Come Small Wonder - Old Thunder Can`t He See That
 He`s Wrong?<P>

 Bridge
 
 Refrain</I>

